## Ordem de CriaГ§ГЈo Recomendada

Seguir esta sequГЄncia evita dependГЄncias circulares e facilita o desenvolvimento incremental:

```
1. Domain/Primitives/     в†’ Result, Error, ErrorType, EntityBase
2. Domain/Entities/       в†’ entidades + validators          [skill: entity-domain]
3. Application/Common/    в†’ IRepository, PagedResult, IUnitOfWork
4. Infrastructure/Data/   в†’ AppDbContext, EfRepository, Configurations  [skill: repository-efcore]
5. Application/Behaviors/ в†’ ValidationBehavior, LoggingBehavior
6. Application/Use Cases/ в†’ Commands + Queries + Handlers   [skill: use-case-cqrs]
7. Api/Models/            в†’ ApiProblemDetails, BaseApiController  [skill: api-controller]
8. Api/Controllers/       в†’ controllers especГ­ficos         [skill: api-controller]
9. Api/Extensions/        в†’ observabilidade, DI             [skill: observability-setup]
10. Dockerfile + compose  в†’ containerizaГ§ГЈo                  [skill: docker-setup]
11. tests/Unit/           в†’ testes unitГЎrios                 [skill: unit-test-scaffold]
```

