## CriaГ§ГЈo da SoluГ§ГЈo вЂ” Comandos CLI

```bash
# 1. Criar soluГ§ГЈo e projetos
dotnet new sln -n MySolution
dotnet new webapi -n Api --framework net9.0 --no-openapi -o src/Api
dotnet new classlib -n Application --framework net9.0 -o src/Application
dotnet new classlib -n Domain --framework net9.0 -o src/Domain
dotnet new classlib -n Infrastructure --framework net9.0 -o src/Infrastructure
dotnet new xunit -n Unit.Tests --framework net9.0 -o tests/Unit

# 2. Adicionar Г  soluГ§ГЈo
dotnet sln add src/Api/Api.csproj
dotnet sln add src/Application/Application.csproj
dotnet sln add src/Domain/Domain.csproj
dotnet sln add src/Infrastructure/Infrastructure.csproj
dotnet sln add tests/Unit/Unit.Tests.csproj

# 3. ReferГЄncias entre projetos
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj reference src/Application/Application.csproj
dotnet add src/Application/Application.csproj reference src/Domain/Domain.csproj
dotnet add src/Infrastructure/Infrastructure.csproj reference src/Application/Application.csproj
dotnet add src/Infrastructure/Infrastructure.csproj reference src/Domain/Domain.csproj
dotnet add tests/Unit/Unit.Tests.csproj reference src/Application/Application.csproj
dotnet add tests/Unit/Unit.Tests.csproj reference src/Domain/Domain.csproj

# 4. Pacotes NuGet вЂ” Domain
dotnet add src/Domain/Domain.csproj package FluentValidation

# 5. Pacotes NuGet вЂ” Application
dotnet add src/Application/Application.csproj package MediatR
dotnet add src/Application/Application.csproj package FluentValidation.DependencyInjectionExtensions
dotnet add src/Application/Application.csproj package AutoMapper

# 6. Pacotes NuGet вЂ” Infrastructure
dotnet add src/Infrastructure/Infrastructure.csproj package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer
dotnet add src/Infrastructure/Infrastructure.csproj package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Design

# 7. Pacotes NuGet вЂ” Api
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj package Serilog.AspNetCore
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj package Serilog.Formatting.Compact
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj package OpenTelemetry.Extensions.Hosting
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj package OpenTelemetry.Instrumentation.AspNetCore
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj package Asp.Versioning.Mvc
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj package Swashbuckle.AspNetCore
dotnet add src/Api/Api.csproj package AspNetCore.HealthChecks.SqlServer

# 8. Pacotes NuGet вЂ” Testes
dotnet add tests/Unit/Unit.Tests.csproj package Moq
dotnet add tests/Unit/Unit.Tests.csproj package Bogus
dotnet add tests/Unit/Unit.Tests.csproj package FluentAssertions
dotnet add tests/Unit/Unit.Tests.csproj package Microsoft.Extensions.Logging.Abstractions
